snippet.title: Day 41 of Note Ban: Many ATMs and Banks are Still Cashless

localized.description:
Day 41 of Demonetisation: No respite in sight as many ATMs and banks are still cashless. People are standing in long queues outside banks and ATMs to withdraw cash.
